

Rooms Setup:


name:
intro: Copy containing an intro for when the user enters the room
encounter: Copy and mob generation if there is combat in this room
combat: function to run through the combat
options: the options for actions that can be taken in a room






COMBAT LOGIC:

start round:

are there any mobs left alive?
    > NO - you are victorious
    > YES - new combatRound


CombatRound:

is chat alive?

    Yes - Mob Attack

        is char still alive?
            Yes? CharAttack
            No? You are dead


    No - You are Dead


    Mobs Attack
    Is chat still alive?
        > NO - you are dead
        > Yes - Char Attack

Char Attack
    >goto start round




